Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:39.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Moritaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:55.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the third year of middle school, the last year of compulsory education,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:04:00.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,adults are always asking us what our dreams are for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:04.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,As for me, Mashiro Moritaka, I answer:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:06.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,“I don't know.”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:08.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,“I still haven't decided.”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:12.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's considered {\i1}normal{\i0} to move onto a better high school, to the best possible university,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and then on to the best company possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:18.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just live life normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.48,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)\c&H6DB9C3&\3c&H393D3C&\fnCopperplate Gothic Bold\pos(180,226)}Tanikusa City\N{\fs18}Akehi\NMiddle School
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:22.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why even though I find it easier to keep myself busy with games and computer stuff at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:24.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I still go to school every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:27.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to cause problems for my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:30.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be called a recluse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:33.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be called a “permanent part-timer”.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:37.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll take the normal route into society, and become a salaryman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:37.67,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H93D3D9&\3c&H506833&\4c&H506833&\shad1\b1\pos(387,59)\fnRockwell}Tosho News
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:37.67,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\shad0\bord0\c&H649751&\b1\fnVerdana\pos(388,158)}National Book Report Contest
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:37.67,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\fscx110\shad0\bord0\c&H649751&\b1\pos(388,200)\fnVerdana}Results Announced{\i1}!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:37.67,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\shad1\bord1\b1\pos(388,326)\fnVerdana\c&H87D7DD&\3c&H464F52&\4c&H464F52&}Congratulations to Takagi Akito-kun{\i1}!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:40.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who'll jump to the top at those places
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:43.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,are the ones who're getting good grades now and have a high rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:48.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The rankings are already fixed, so the future will be nothing more than an extension of the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A boring future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:53.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is tiresome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:05:00.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my outlook on life, having lived these last 14 years as a good kid should.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:03.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something in a book I just read,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:09.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,that the greatest event, the highest purpose of life, is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:15.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some crap said by a womanizing adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:20.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,For me, who can't even talk to the girl he likes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:23.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,love is just sad and painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:26.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fruitless love...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:29.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,that will cast me into the abyss once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:33.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please work hard for your mid-terms tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:41.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:42.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y–Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:45.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou! Suzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:46.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:49.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tests start tomorrow huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:52.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:53.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can head home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's just use that time well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:57.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:58.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:01.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:04.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lonely without you in my class!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:05.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off, Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:11.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:12.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:14.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to see a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:16.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! That hot one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:17.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:19.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:19.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you Saikou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:22.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to wind up in the bottom half of the ranking board.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:24.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:25.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:27.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou! He's no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:32.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:34.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My math notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:43.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can study without my notes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't want to leave them at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:53.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi Akito...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:55.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:58.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be studying to protect your number one spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:03.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he find out I have a crush on Azuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:06.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make such a serious face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:09.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:12.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have your hands on my notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I sit all the way in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:23.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you drawing something in this notebook during class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:25.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I knew that you'd come back for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:28.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I took the liberty of looking inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:31.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure you'd come back for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:34.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:36.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is he planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:39.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway these are good, Azuki Miho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:43.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's quiet, so she doesn't stand out, but she's top class for this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Takagi have a thing for her too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:47.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Azuki probably has a crush on you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:50.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:53.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,N–No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:56.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't even talked yet, and first of all what makes you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:07:58.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I explain that to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:08:00.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I sit all the way in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:04.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,As if you can understand everything about the class just because you sit in the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:05.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:11.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if it were the case that the person in question did not feel that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:14.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd freely admit that my instincts have their limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:15.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:17.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he so happy about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:23.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return your notebook and I won't tell anyone your secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:26.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:31.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:33.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There is one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:35.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:37.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll definitely tell me to stay away from Azuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:42.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Work with me and become a mangaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:46.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've loved manga ever since I was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:48.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I've always dreamed of becoming a mangaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:52.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've considered many others, but I need your art!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:55.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're ranked top-class academically, even at the national level,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:56.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and you want to be a mangaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:09:01.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it not the desire of men to achieve greatness?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:02.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To get rich?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:07.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have neither the looks nor the singing ability to enter the world of show business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:09.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no extraordinary skill in sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:12.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have literary talent, and you can draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:15.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, what is there but manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:18.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan's manga is already world renowned as a great culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:21.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,650)}Let's leave our mark on the world with manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:29.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You, who have won awards for your papers and compositions, will write the stories,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:30.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I will draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:34.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:34.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:38.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,“But I refuse,” huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:42.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You too are quite the manga lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:45.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't become a mangaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:50.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Only that tiny fraction of people born with true talent and genius can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:52.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond that, it's just gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:53.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gambling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:55.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,When you say “mangaka,”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:58.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,you're talking about someone who can make a living off of nothing but drawing manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:01.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you get your work serialized in a weekly publication,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:04.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be ranked every week through reader surveys,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and if it's not popular enough you'll be dropped after ten weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:12.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hit it big or churn out multiple volumes of reasonably popular manga that's one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:15.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you can't do that then you're just a gambler.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:18.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Only 0.001% of those who try actually make their fortune in manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:20.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's about 1 in 100,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:22.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with the probability theories?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:23.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd you hear that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My uncle was a mangaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:33.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he was just a gambler.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:37.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... {\i1}was{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:45.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your uncle was a mangaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:47.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:48.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:49.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who? What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:53.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a long time ago, and even if I tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:55.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:59.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Kawaguchi Tarou, and he used to write in Shonen Ju—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:00.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He wrote "Chou Hero Densetsu"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.96,TL Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: Chou Hero Densetsu = Super Hero Legend
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to watch the anime when I was a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:06.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought the manga volumes, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:08.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really love his manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:10.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That settles it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the DNA of a mangaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:14.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know a lot about manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:17.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's something we want to know, we can just ask your uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:19.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What DNA? He was my uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:28.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, Kawaguchi Tarou's art was horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:32.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:34.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess DNA has nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:36.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm not going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:39.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's your condition, then I don't need the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:41.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, you thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be a gamble,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:46.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but you'll never win the lottery if you don't buy a ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:48.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't make manga, then you'll never make it big!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:51.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way are you more likely to get the ¥300,000,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My uncle also used to say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:57.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:03.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, book reports and manga are completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:04.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:09.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote my compositions after carefully calculating the best way to earn the approval of the judges.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:12.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I just have to aim to earn the approval of publishers and readers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:15.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you aim for the Naoki Prize?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:15.17,TL Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: The Naoki Prize is an award held semiannually for upcoming novelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:20.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, right now manga makes more money, and I like it better anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:21.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel the dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:25.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you draw the art yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:27.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They have classes for people trying to make original work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You could apply for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:29.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:31.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to get a job as a public servant
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:33.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,or an employee in a stable company or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:36.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't know about my future...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:37.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why would you refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:40.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:43.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, I'm not really sure myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:46.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess... it's too much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:52.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going home to study now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:53.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:01.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just going to coast through life like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you want out of life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:06.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,People like you, who are already working towards their dreams in their third year, are more unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:09.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's best to start early!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:12.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else just can't decide what they want and they go through life dragging their feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:15.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I, we can definitely do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:17.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:21.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go home and think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:23.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:25.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think the answer's going to be, “No.”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:26.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:28.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think it over carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:29.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If your answer's still “no”, then I'll give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:36.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to become a mangaka when I was in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:40.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why did you become a mangaka, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:42.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still just a gambler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:44.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you become a gambler?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:47.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to become popular with girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mangaka are popular with girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:55.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that if I became famous and rich, that would make me popular, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:02.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in middle school, there was this girl I liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:08.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I graduated, having barely spoken with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:10.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a short story!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:13.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But on the day of graduation, I received a letter from that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:15.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A love letter! Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:21.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, all she wrote was stuff like, “Let's both do our best from now on.”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:27.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I wrote her a reply saying, “Yes, let's both work hard.”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:30.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We went to different high schools,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:33.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,so we just exchanged letters like those without even seeing one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:35.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, that's actually kinda nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:41.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, after graduating high school she got into a top corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:43.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to a fourth-rate college.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:46.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had gotten it into my head that I wanted to marry her, so I thought to myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:48.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,“Things can't keep going like this,”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:51.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,“I want to do something to earn her approval.”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:51.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was thinking when—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:54.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You became a mangaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But she became the president's secretary,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:02.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was a beginner mangaka with doubtful prospects.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:05.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like the gap between us was growing day by day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:08.09,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord4\b0\fscx130\fs26\shad0\c&H555976&\3c&H91B8BB&\4c&H555976&\shad1\fnShakeAndBake\move(507,-36,507,60,0,3533)\frz16.898\fad(400,0)}Chou Hero Densetsu{}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:08.09,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz13.764\fscx100\fscy100\frx14\fry348\c&H56506E&\shad0\bord3\3c&HD4D8E1&\move(496,104,496,204)} TV Anime On the Air
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:08.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, when "Chou Hero Densetsu" became an anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.33,0:15:09.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You confessed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:11.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She married someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:13.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:16.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have lost the gamble for her love,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:19.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but she was the reason I was able to try so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:22.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But two years later...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:29.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:32.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:34.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it really was sudden, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:36.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what could have caused it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:39.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he was under a lot of stress...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:42.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But he wasn't even all that busy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:45.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he had a lot of debts. Also—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:47.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:49.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Nobuhiro appreciates it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:52.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,O–Oh... I'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:04.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the seven years after "Chou hero Densetsu", my uncle wrote two more series,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:06.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but they were quickly canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:11.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They told me he died of overwork, but I thought he committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:15.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I had a dream, there was nothing I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:18.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it just won't come to pass, then I might as well live like everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:20.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Moritaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:22.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:24.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:27.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I think you're home, you go out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:29.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:31.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a test tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:33.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never get into Minami High with that kind of attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:36.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:40.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single person is just saying whatever the hell they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:42.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave my future...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:43.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the hell alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's me, Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:54.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi? How did you get this number?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:56.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it from Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:57.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:17:00.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, I'm going to Azuki's house now to confess to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:01.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I want you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:04.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know I like her, so why—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:06.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't come, there's no point!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:08.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:09.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:10.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you I don't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you confess on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:15.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:18.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I love your art, and I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:19.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:21.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're confessing to the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:24.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I looked a bit into Azuki and I found out something amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:26.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to attend your confession?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that, just get here quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:29.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at the convenience store in Nishi-chou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:34.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:35.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting, Saikou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:37.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not “Saikou,” it's “Moritaka.”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:38.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:39.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:39.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,H–Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:44.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice house, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:46.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A house fit for a madonna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:47.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,H–Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever even pressed the doorbell of a girl's house before?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:54.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:55.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have then push it for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:56.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:58.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your confession after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:01.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:03.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He pushed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:04.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to play doorbell dash with me, you bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:08.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:12.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,U–Um, this is Takagi. I'm in the same class as Miho.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.64,0:18:16.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something I wanted to ask Miho about tomorrow's test.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:17.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:18.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:20.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The top student for the year?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:22.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, ah... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:25.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, she knows his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:27.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:28.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:32.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's kinda suspicious of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:34.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:36.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, Azuki's voice! Aw, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:37.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:38.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:39.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:40.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you step outside for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something very important to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:45.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:48.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, she's going to come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:49.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what her casual clothes are like!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:52.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let her know that I'm here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:53.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,S–Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:55.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to blow a fuse here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:14.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:17.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:20.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I... am going to become a mangaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:23.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to confess that to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:24.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what he meant by “confess”?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:28.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from your friend, Miyoshi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:31.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki-san, you're trying to become a voice actor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:32.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Voice actor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,“Yeah”? Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:38.86,Main top,,0000,0000,0000,,You even took some voice recordings you recorded yourself to a production office, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:39.86,Main top,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really doing your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:41.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, a fantasy? Could she really be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:43.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And they said you were really good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:49.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Azuki going to become a voice actor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:52.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, next, a word from Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:55.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:58.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:01.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:07.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I–I'm going to be drawing the art, and he's doing the stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:08.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:11.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Then I'm sure you'll make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:14.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Her eyes are shining! Her eyes are all sparkly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:15.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:19.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,S–So if our manga gets turned into an anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:21.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,then we'll reserve the role of heroine for you or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:22.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:23.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:25.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:28.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a voice actor and appear on your anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:29.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:32.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what a smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:34.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at me, and so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:37.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute, Azuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:41.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in middle school there was this girl I liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to marry her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:50.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So if that dream comes true, please marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:05.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:07.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was remembering what my uncle said...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:11.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, this is so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:12.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:13.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:14.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:17.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure what to say but just now, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:18.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:19.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:21.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Promise what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:23.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't mean the marriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:26.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.79,0:21:29.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But only if the dream comes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:32.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then I won't see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:38.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, um... The manga becomes an anime, and you do the voice work,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:41.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,then we suddenly get married without so much as seeing each other once?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:45.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Until the dream comes true we have to work with no distractions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.52,0:21:48.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then we'll just encourage one another through mail or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.53,0:21:49.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:53.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's fine! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:55.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, mom is coming! Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:21:58.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.59,0:22:01.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, I understand, uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:04.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}So this is what it was like for the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.85,0:22:09.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I promised to get married if my dream comes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.23,0:22:12.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,700)}Aren't the terms of the bet better for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:16.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will become a mangaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.21,0:22:18.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah! This is even better than I planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:20.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's become Japan's top mangakas!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:23.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, aiming for the top is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.04,0:22:26.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In this rapidly aging society, it will be impossible to overtake the likes of Dragon Ball and One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:30.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a logical analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.25,0:22:32.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I haven't decided whether to join you or not.
