Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:36.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.43,0:22:39.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely become a mangaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:43.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll marry Azuki!
